!! Quick Commands

If you're comfortable with browser console, you can also switch themes with:

```javascript
// Switch to dark theme
$tw.wiki.addTiddler({title: "$:/theme", text: "$:/themes/pmu/monokai-pro-dark"});

// Switch to light theme
$tw.wiki.addTiddler({title: "$:/theme", text: "$:/themes/pmu/monokai-pro-light"});
```
